         <abstract id="aspace_2213c3a4c32ae7828f220565e9b625d2">The records consist of photographic slides used in the "Class of 1963 40th Reunion Collage," as well as a copy of the final production on videotape (VHS). Also includes a DVD of "In Our Own Words: Yale '63 at Fifty", a film of interviews with members of the Class of 1963 at their 50th reunion.  The material documents the members of the Yale College Class of 1963.</abstract>
