      <scopecontent id="aspace_b022b4418355172c204928ec1099e62a">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The records consist of photographic slides used in the "Class of 1963 40th Reunion Collage," as well as a copy of the final production on videotape (VHS). Also includes a DVD of "In Our Own Words: Yale '63 at Fifty", a film of interviews with members of the Class of 1963 at their 50th reunion.  The material documents the members of the Yale College Class of 1963.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
